    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "In the 1950s, divers uncovered a remarkably preserved prehistoric hunter and seven other humans in the spring’s depths.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        6
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://www.wmslss.org/the-springs/"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "During the middle Archaic period, 6,000‑7,500 years ago, the spring served as a mortuary pond where peat buried its earliest Floridians.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        8
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://www.wmslss.org/the-springs/"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "Warm Mineral Springs is fed by a free‑flowing artesian spring that has been a natural wonder for millennia.",
